A collection of stand-alone AWS Boto scripts written in python
http://boto.readthedocs.org/en/latest/index.html

Disclaimer:
These scripts have been writen for specific requirements - they are tested to work - however 
they are only provided to aid you in creating scripts specific to your own environment.

I suggest you test these first before using on anything that resembles production environment.
Or better yet re-write them for your own purpose!

Pull Requests are most welcome!